    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system that provides seamless valve timing across the entire rev range. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This specimen features a structurally reinforced rear subframe\u2014addressing the chassis's primary weak point\u2014and retains its factory-spec suspension geometry with zero bushing compliance. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard. This is a turnkey, concours-level machine for the driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
