      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines showroom quality. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a mirror-finish exterior completely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the premium leather retains its original scent and supple texture, with no visible wear on the bolsters or tactile controls. Every electronic feature and safety system functions flawlessly. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a comprehensive binder of service records that documents preventative maintenance exceeding factory recommendations. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a specimen that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Inspections are welcome; the quality speaks for itself.",
